  "text": "This assumption will be formulated more precisely below. It is, on the one hand, absolutely necessary for the validity of (4.1) at least in the case of rational CFT [CITATION_1] 6 . The assumption above is, on the other hand, a rather deep statement about a given vertex algebra V from the mathematical point of view, especially if V is not rational.",
